ygData.messageBody:
Honestly I have been soloing sister island since 12th level. now 17th now
I just go there for money I can clear about 100 pp in 4 hours outta there.
You most likely will not get any xp from it. Consider hunting aviaks in
south karanas. Or maybe Najena.
Aarkon
17th level Necromancer
Povar server.
